title: Wild Cajun Meals LLC Recalls Frozen, Fully Cooked Jambalaya and Gumbo Products Produced without Benefit of Inspection
summary: Editor’s note: On January 31, 2023, FSIS was notified that the recalled product did not enter retail stores in the state of Arkansas. The recall release has been updated to reflect Louisiana and Texas as the only states receiving this product. WASHINGTON, Jan. 30, 2023...
impacted_products: 32-oz. Plastic containers of “Lady Jambalaya Homemade Jambalaya.”
32-oz. Plastic containers of “Lady Jambalaya Homemade Gumbo.”
